ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Manitoba livestock producers Assistance Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to Manitoba livestock producers faced with feed availability issues due to excessive rainfall and flooding through a contribution under the federal component of the 2010 Manitoba feed and transportation assistance.
